  "title": "Senior Sales",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will apply your sales expertise in Kitchen Appliances and Consumer Electronics to manage both traditional and modern trade/project sales, building strong client relationships and driving revenue growth.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and execute sales strategies to expand company’s customer base and to ensure its growing presence. </li><li>Manage client accounts and projects to meet monthly retail sales targets </li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 3 to 5 years of sales experience in Kitchen Appliances or Consumer Electronics handling traditional and modern trade/project sales</li><li>Bilingual proficiency in English and Mandarin to communicate with diverse client groups</li><li>Possession of a car to facilitate client visits and sales activities</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>Basic salary $3,000 to $4,000 plus commission ranging from $2,000 to $6,000</li><li>Petrol reimbursement up to $880</li></ul>",
